## LangGraph Workflow (Interactive Mode)

The interactive pipeline is built with LangGraph's `StateGraph`, providing a directed acyclic graph (DAG) with one conditional loop for retry logic.

### Graph Definition

Built in [workflow.py](backend/app/agents/workflow.py):

```
EntryPoint
    │
    ▼
build_context ──────────────────────┐
    │                               │
    ▼                               │ (on validation errors, retry_count < 3)
generate_sql ──► validate_sql ──────► increment_retry ──┐
    │                       │                           │
    │               ┌───────┴───────┐                   │
    │               │               │                   │
    │         "execute_sql"    "error" (retry exhausted)│
    │               │                                   │
    │               ▼                                   │
    │        create_table                               │
    │               │                                   │
    │               ▼                                   │
    │        generate_insights                          │
    │               │                                   │
    └───────────────┼───────────────────────────────────┘
                    ▼
                   END
```

### Conditional Routing Logic

`should_retry(state)` in [workflow.py:57-65](backend/app/agents/workflow.py#L57-L65):

```
if validation_errors is empty → "execute_sql"
elif retry_count < 3          → "retry" (loop back to generate_sql)
else                          → "error" (terminate with END)
```

### State Schema

Defined in [state.py](backend/app/core/state.py). The `WorkflowState` TypedDict tracks the full pipeline state:

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `user_query` | `str` | User's natural-language question |
| `system_prompt` | `str` | Fully rendered system prompt (with injected metadata) |
| `generated_sql` | `Optional[str]` | LLM-generated Oracle SQL |
| `validation_errors` | `List[str]` | Errors from the SQL validator |
| `retry_count` | `int` | Number of retry attempts |
| `raw_data` | `List[dict]` | Query result rows from Oracle |
| `execution_error` | `Optional[str]` | Error message if execution failed |
| `created_table` | `Optional[str]` | Name of created MariaDB table |
| `final_insights` | `List[str]` | Generated executive summary bullets |
| `status` | `str` | Pipeline status: `starting`, `success`, `error`, `no_data`, `table_created` |

