Prompt for the `generate_insights` node. Instructs the LLM to produce exactly 3 bullet points (max 25 words each) suitable for an executive CFO summary. Rules: focus on financial insight (totals, trends, outliers, risks), no methodology descriptions, use absolute numbers and percentages.

