## Running the Project

### Start the API Server

```bash
cd backend
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8119
# or
python -m app.main
```

### Run the Ageing ETL (CLI)

```bash
cd backend
python -m app.etl.build_ageing_report                  # Full run
python -m app.etl.build_ageing_report --dry-run         # Preview only
python -m app.etl.build_ageing_report --target MY_TABLE  # Custom table
```

### Test Oracle Connection

```bash
python test_oracle_connection.py
```

### Exit Codes (ETL)

| Code | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| 0 | Success |
| 1 | Empty data (no rows extracted) |
| 2 | Database error (SQLAlchemyError) |
| 3 | Unexpected error |

